              Day-1
  
What is linux? 
      Linux is an open-source operating system like windows,Mac os,iOS , Android etc....

Again what is operating system
       Operating system is nothing but a software that enables communication between hardware and software
Applications -> shell -> kernel -> Hardware
 
 "Linux kernel" is the core part of the operating system....It establishes a communication between device and and software..It sends the input to the processor to get processed and brings output to the hardware to display it.
°device management
°memory management
°processor management 
   
*Reasons to learn linux 
1.It is flexible and stable operating system
2.It is effective for programming
3.different linux versions are available 
